name: ultrafiltration module production, hollow fiber | ultrafiltration module | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/12089/documentation

This dataset represents the production of  ultrafiltration membrane module and housing. This dataset is based on PALL UNA-620A modules and is considered to have 50 m2 of active surface per module.    

From reception of raw materials for production of membrane module. 

This dataset ends with production of module for ultrafiltration process. This dataset only includes material inputs for production. Losses and processing for materials have been excluded due to lack of data. Thus no waste are considered. Production energy is also excluded due to lack of  data.
category: E:Water supply; sewerage, waste management and remediation activities/36:Water collection, treatment and supply/360:Water collection, treatment and supply/3600:Water collection, treatment and supply

processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription: From one of ultrafiltration module to all ultrafiltration modules available on the market. Extrapolation was achived using literature data (articles, patent, spec sheets, etc.)
processDocumentation.samplingDescription: General rules for inventories for hollow fiber ultrafiltration modules are derived from data from technical drawings, patents and technical litterature.
